list.abstract: Month（英 [mʌnθ]，美 [mʌnθ]），英语单词，作名词为月；一个月的时间；四周。短语搭配有last month（上个月）。例句为“He paid the water bill last month.（他上个月付了水费。）”

yingyinNormal.en: I knew it. What month? December. Say it again. Whoa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就知道，哪个月？十二月。再说一遍。哇。

yingyinNormal.en: We're booked solid for the next month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们下个月全部都被订满了。

yingyinNormal.en: This month that's you. Congratulations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个月送的是你，恭喜你被选中。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, how long will it take to make? A month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那要多久才能配好？一个月。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: But her birthday isn't like for another month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是一个月后才是她生日啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Every month, the Box sends up a new arrival.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个月，笼子里都会送来一个新人。

yingyinNormal.en: Your members of Congress are home this month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个月，各位所在地方的议员还在家乡休假。

yingyinNormal.en: Twenty bucks says they're married within the month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我赌二十块钱，他们一个月内就会结婚。

yingyinNormal.en: Didn't you see Taylor Swift twice this month?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你这个月看了两次泰勒·斯威夫特的演唱会吧？{她的歌词以女孩恋爱/分手后的心情为主}

yingyinNormal.en: Last month, our businesses added 236,000 new jobs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上个月,我们的经济创造了236,000新的就业岗位。

yingyinNormal.en: Last month, our businesses created 314,000 new jobs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上个月，我们的经济创造了314,000个新的就业岗位。

yingyinNormal.en: On average, they're paying just $82 a month for coverage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 平均下来,他们每月仅仅需要支付$82。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, let's ask my wall of 374 consecutive employee-of-the-month awards.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我们问问我的连续374届获得月度最佳员工的记录墙吧！

yingyinNormal.en: We're on the cover this month, but next month it could be you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们本月上了封面，但下个月就可以是你。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? You know what? I think we're making too big a deal out of this. Okay? So we'll pay our bills late this month. And maybe next month we'll cut back on a few things.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得我们太小题大作了。我们这个月会比较紧，下个月我们就节省一些开销。

yingyinNormal.en: Ross, please trust me. I buy 30 fashion magazines a month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 信我，我一个月买30本时尚杂志。

yingyinNormal.en: Someone had to have spent a whole month in the Glade, alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总得有人独自在这儿呆上一个月。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I don't get this. A month ago, these people were my friends.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个月前他们是我朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: Where's he off to? Utah for a month to plan his wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他要去哪？犹他州，去那一个月准备婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. My sweater. I've been looking for this for like a month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的毛衣，我找这件毛衣找了一个月。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 每月一次的；每月的；按月的

word_family.mean: n. 月；一个月的时间；四周；太阴月；朔望月；二十八天

sense_info_list.en: a period of time between the same dates in successive calendar months

examination_example.sentence: However, over the past 12 <highlight>months</highlight>, those commuters have also experienced some of the worst rail strikes in years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，在过去的12个月里，这些通勤者也经历了一些近年来最严重的铁路罢工。

examination_example.sentence: It takes about three weeks to a <highlight>month</highlight> to notice significant changes in your weight due to altering your training program.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大约需要三周到一个月的时间来注意到由于改变训练计划而导致的体重的显著变化。

examination_example.sentence: A Canadian study found that children as young as 14 <highlight>months</highlight> can differentiate between a credible person and a dishonest one.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 加拿大的一项研究发现，14个月大的孩子就能区分开一个可信的人和一个不诚实的人。

sense_info_list.en: each of the twelve named periods into which a year is divided

examination_example.sentence: One example of how artists and scientists have together rocked the scenes came last <highlight>month</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是艺术家和科学家在上个月共同震撼现场的一个例子。

examination_example.sentence: At any given point, I should have deep work scheduled for roughly the next <highlight>month</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在任何时候，我都应该在大约下个月安排深入的工作。

examination_example.sentence: In contrast to France's actions, Denmark's fashion industry agreed last <highlight>month</highlight> on rules and sanctions regarding the age, health, and other characteristics of models.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与法国的做法形成对比的是，丹麦时装业上个月就模特的年龄、健康和其他特征达成了规定和约束。
